author: Soo Kim
title: Confirmed Coronavirus Cases Worldwide Pass One Million After Doubling in Less Than a Week
description: The COVID-19 virus has spread to at least 181 countries and regions, including more than 236,000 confirmed infections in the U.S., the global epicenter of the outbreak.
content:
The coronavirus has infected more than a million people around the world, according to the latest figures from Johns Hopkins University.
